description: Maiyet is a modern luxury brand that combines the contemporary design of its dresses, pants and shirts with the heritage of the world's master artisans. The brand is deeply committed to forging partnerships that promote business growth in global economies, reviving ancient techniques like Javanese Batik, preserving the hand-operated jacquard loom for silks, sourcing the finest cashmere from nomadic herders in Mongolia and promoting sustainable employment. Made in USA.
title: 3/4-length shorts

description: EXCLUSIVE AT NET-A-PORTER.COM. As temperatures start to drop, we begin our search for the perfect winter coat and this year, fuzzy styles are at the top of our list. Stella McCartney's cream faux shearling version has a cool '70s feel and extra long sleeves that reach your knuckles. It's lined in lustrous satin so fits smoothly over sweaters and blouses.
title: Faux Shearling Coat - Cream

description: Whether it's a new PB or an extra mile on the treadmill, we all have our own version of gold to strive for, and APL Athletic Propulsion Labs' metallic sneakers bring that dream one step closer. They're made from the brand's innovative four-way stretch TechLoom mesh and set on cushioned Propelium™ midsoles to help absorb shock and protect joints. Switch your laces for the accompanying glittering set for added motivation.
title: Techloom Pro Metallic Mesh Sneakers - Gold

description: Athletic Propulsion Labs' 'TechLoom Phantom' sneakers are made from flexible, breathable mesh with four-way stretch. Complete with a neoprene tongue and integrated collar, this gray pair has a Propelium™ midsole to regenerate energy and a grooved base for traction. They're perfect for training on hard surfaces, like pavement or concrete.
title: Techloom Phantom 3d Mesh Sneakers - Gray
